msgstr "디스크 스왑 크기"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:919
msgid "Custom size (GB)"
msgstr "사용자 지정 크기 (GB)"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:929
msgid ""
"zswap uses compressed RAM as a cache and spills to a disk swap file when "
"full."
msgstr ""
"zswap은 압축된 메모리를 캐시로 사용하며, 가득 차면 디스크의 스왑 파일로 넘깁"
"니다."

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:946
msgid "All data on the selected drive will be erased."
msgstr "선택한 드라이브의 모든 데이터가 삭제됩니다."

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:969
msgid "System Setup"
msgstr "시스템 설정"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:976
#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1104
msgid "Timezone"
msgstr "시간대"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:989
msgid "Administrator account (sudo)"
msgstr "관리자 계정 (sudo)"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:996
msgid "Root Password (optional)"
msgstr "root 비밀번호 (선택 사항)"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1021
msgid "Install Apps"
msgstr "앱 설치"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1028
msgid ""
"These apps are pre-downloaded and will be copied during install. Uncheck any "
"you don't want."
msgstr ""
"이 앱들은 미리 다운로드되어 있으며 설치 중에 복사됩니다. 원하지 않는 앱은 선"
"택을 해제하세요."

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1085
msgid "Ready to Install"
msgstr "설치 준비 완료"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1091
msgid "Review your settings and click Install to begin."
msgstr "설정을 확인한 후 '설치'를 클릭하여 시작하세요."

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1098
msgid "Network"
msgstr "네트워크"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1101
msgid "Memory"
msgstr "메모리"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1102
msgid "Name"
msgstr "이름"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1105
msgid "Administrator"
msgstr "관리자"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1106
msgid "Root password"
msgstr "root 비밀번호"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1107
msgid "Apps"
msgstr "앱"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1126
msgid "Installing..."
msgstr "설치 중..."

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1149
msgid "Skip"
msgstr "건너뛰기"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1156
msgid "Retry"
msgstr "재시도"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1163
msgid "Reboot"
msgstr "재부팅"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1276
msgid "No networks found."
msgstr "네트워크를 찾을 수 없습니다."

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1303
msgid "Strong"
msgstr "강함"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1305
msgid "Medium"
msgstr "보통"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1307
msgid "Weak"
msgstr "약함"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1311
msgid "Secured"
msgstr "보안됨"

#: ../files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1311
msgid "Open"
msgstr "열림"

